projects.project-name: Chavez Lab Intern at Sanford-Burnham Prebys (2021-present)
projects.description: Analyzed tumor samples using AmpliconArchitect to detect the presence of extrachromosomal DNA, using the bioinformatics cloud platform Cavatica. Extensive experience with Python scripts and bioinformatics data types, such as FASTQ and BAM files.

Built a web application to allow users to find and share recipes. Used React framework, along with HTML, CSS, and Javascript for frontend and backend. I also worked in a large group, and learned Github, merging, and other software team issues.
